# Changelogs

## [0.1.2] 2022-04-12

- added useCompletableRxEffect to be used outside class scope
- updated implementation of rxEffect to accept a Javascript object and destruction methods as parameters

## [0.1.20] 2023-02-21

- Added Reducer & State decorator for providing properties to component for local state management
- Moved hooks to dedicated `hooks.ts` file
- Added `StateComponentType` and `ReducerComponentType` interfaces that must be implemented by component with `@Reducer()` and `@State` decorators
